==注意事項==
與其他許多在[[帝國主義|帝國主義]]時期所進行的普查相同，普查結果顯示當局對民族政策的觀點。例如俄語人口被誇大，<ref name=geifman>[[Anna_Geifman|Anna Geifman]], ''Russia Under the Last Tsar: Opposition and Subversion, 1894-1917'', Wiley-Blackwell, 1999, ISBN 1-55786-995-2, [https://books.google.com/books?id=HBg7tQ7BGY0C&pg=PA118 Google Print, p. 118-119] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HBg7tQ7BGY0C&pg=PA118 |date=20201017123045 }}</ref>波蘭語人口則被低估。<ref>Piotr Eberhardt, Jan Owsinski, ''Ethnic groups and population changes in twentieth-century Central-Eastern Europe'', M.E. Sharpe, 2003, ISBN 0-7656-0665-8, [https://books.google.com/books?id=jLfX1q3kJzgC&pg=RA1-PA27 Google Print, p.27] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jLfX1q3kJzgC&pg=RA1-PA27 |date=20200426002401 }}</ref><ref>Jerzy Borzęcki, ''The Soviet-Polish peace of 1921 and the creation of interwar Europe'', Yale University Press, 2008, ISBN 0-300-12121-0, [https://books.google.com/books?id=wjsk1sdZzdIC&pg=PA10 Google Print, p.10] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wjsk1sdZzdIC&pg=PA10 |date=20200426002405 }}</ref>烏克蘭語及白俄羅斯語則被歸類為俄語的方言，並以「小」俄羅斯語與「白」俄羅斯語的名稱取代。<ref name=geifman/>[[波蘭|波蘭]]作為地名被抹殺，取而代之的是「維斯瓦河地區」；「歐俄」地區除了包含今日的俄羅斯、烏克蘭與白俄羅斯外，還包含[[愛沙尼亞|愛沙尼亞]]、[[拉脫維亞|拉脫維亞]]、[[立陶宛|立陶宛]]與[[比薩拉比亞|比薩拉比亞]]地區。

